<blockquote>
  <p>3D visualisation</p>
</blockquote>

<p>The crystallographic structure of the <sup>H. marismortui</sup> large ribosomal subunit. The 23S rRNA and 5S rRNA are shown in blue and ribosomal proteins are in green. The PTC is highlighted by nucleotides of the 23S rRNA peptidyl transferase loop and shown in red. The figure was generated from the PDB ID:1JJ2 at 2.4 Ã… resolution.</p>

